oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mr. Whipple Job No. 36931
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 1524) for an order placed by Mr. Whipple for 4 orders of 75 two color window cards for a performance by Lefty Frizzell at the Chaparrol Convention Center on June 11 and 12, a performance by the Willis Brothers at the Chaparrol Convention Center on June 25 and 26, a performance by Webb Price at the Chaparrol Convention Center on July 30 and 31, and a performance by Faron Young at the Chaparrol Convention Center on August 13 and 14. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
